      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "- Show security as part of the build and release loop\n- Scan code, validate risky behavior in a sandbox, return findings to developers\n- Fix issues before the agent ships",
      "demo_actions": "- Show the security loop at a high level\n- Cover code scanning, sandbox validation, and returned findings\n- Tie the loop back to the developer workflow",
      "screenshot": null,
      "visual": ".cutready/visuals/ecc6f60b6a05.json",
      "design_plan": "Narrative goal: make row 3 feel like a real security gate in the agent release lifecycle, showing that security is not an afterthought but a continuous loop between developers and release. Hero metaphor: a secure release orbit, with Microsoft Defender as the central checkpoint and three surrounding stages feeding back into developer fixes. Main objects: 1) title and subtitle centered at the top, 2) left stage card labeled Code Scan with a few simple code-line marks, 3) center hero shield card labeled Defender Release Gate, 4) right stage card labeled Sandbox Validate with a small isolated test chamber motif, 5) bottom stage pill labeled Findings -> Dev Fixes -> Ship that closes the loop. Layout: use the full 960x540 canvas; title at y about 64 and subtitle at y about 102; left card around x 96 y 198 width 200 height 120; center hero card around x 355 y 168 width 250 height 170; right card around x 664 y 198 width 200 height 120; bottom pill centered around x 300 y 392 width 360 height 70. Add 3 arrows: left to center, center to right, right curving down toward bottom pill, and bottom arrow back toward left to imply the loop. Semantic color tokens: $background on scene, $title and $subtitle for framing text, $surface for all cards, $border for outlines, $accent for the center Defender gate and key arrows, $foreground for labels, $muted for supporting text, optional $warning for tiny risk markers in the findings pill. Motion beats: beat 1 title and subtitle fade in; beat 2 left and right stage cards rise in together; beat 3 center Defender gate scales/fades in as the hero; beat 4 arrows draw in; beat 5 bottom findings pill appears and final loop settles readable on screen."
    }
